    <node id="Маленький принц">
      <data key="d0">Маленький принц</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">A young boy appearing as an otherworldly visitor from space, whose existence is unexplained and leads to adventures with the narrator.&lt;SEP&gt;Unnamed prince who lived on a planet smaller than himself and desired a companion.&lt;SEP&gt;Unnamed prince who lived on a planet full of plants and creatures, with the ability to understand the significance of small seeds that could become huge baobabs. He was curious about his surroundings, especially the baobabs and their impact.&lt;SEP&gt;Unnamed prince who lived on a planet full of plants and creatures, with the ability to understand the significance of small seeds that could become huge baobabs. He was also able to draw pictures to help others understand the importance.&lt;SEP&gt;Unnamed prince who lived on a planet full of plants and creatures, with the ability to understand the significance of small seeds that could become huge baobabs. He tried to warn others about the potential dangers of baobabs.&lt;SEP&gt;Unnamed prince who lived on a planet full of plants and creatures, with the ability to understand the significance of small seeds that could become huge baobabs. He warned about the dangers of baobabs.</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-265544bb40b451cd313707a2a4b33ff4-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-6b2ba88f29d6d77fed85771bc5dc9981-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-adc6c168dbb425d9ece24d5bc28b2fcc-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-1b8b1d20aa2c3a367e6898ef909e1830-chunk-000</data>
